OSOGBO – Speaker Osun State House of Assembly, Timothy Owoeye, has called on Nigerians to put behind the negativities of the outgoing year and forge ahead with hope that year 2021 will be a year of prosperity. Owowye gave the charge in a New Year message issued through his Chief Press Sec­retary, Kunle Alabi He held that People and Governments at all levels must strive to ensure that the New year herald a speedy re­covery of the economy. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! Owoeye stressed that resi­dents and citizens must wait in hopes that all that was lost with happenings of the pre­vious year will be recouped through hard work and per­severance. He stated that the 7th As­sembly under his watch in Osun while passing the year 2021 Appropriation bill into law ensured that it is a bud­get that will bring dividend of democracy and prosperity to the people of the State. Diri Signs N329.29bn 2021 Bayelsa Budget Into Law Udu Youths Commend Okowa, Uviejitobor Over Development His words, “In Osun, the House of Assembly in collabo­ration with Governor Oyetola led executive provides that the 2021 budget focused strongly on post COVID-19 recovery with huge investments in the economy and a whopping sum of N1.4bn budgeted for Youth Developmental pro­grammes. “The House of Assembly in her resolve to ensure that the New year is better charged implementing Ministries and agencies not to dampen the morale of the Assembly by continually working hard to deliver on all the compo­nents of the budget for the betterment of our people as we put behind us all that has happened in year 2020. “The resolve of the As­sembly to strengthen its oversight mechanism in 2021 is like never before, we will be holding quarterly budget performance interaction with MDAs as well as sustaining public engagement to enable it get factual feedback from our People. “I want to charge us all not to lose focus, we will have to pursue that which we have missed and lost last year, I am of the assurance that if we put our hearts to it, we will surely overtake and recover in many folds in the New year”. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION